text: Komsomolsky () is a rural locality (a settlement) in Akhtubinsky Selsoviet, Krasnoyarsky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 1,175 as of 2010. There are 8 streets. == Geography == It is located on the Akhtuba River. == References == Category:Rural localities in Krasnoyarsky District, Astrakhan Oblast
title: Komsomolsky, Astrakhan Oblast
